flowchart LR
    subgraph 資料來源["📥 資料來源 (Data Sources)"]
        A1[API 拉取]
        A2[IoT 感測器]
        A3[CSV/JSON 批次]
        A4[網頁爬取]
        A5[事件推送\nWebhook]
    end

    subgraph Bronze["🟤 Bronze Layer\n（原始落地，不清理）"]
        B[Raw Storage\nData Lake]
    end

    subgraph Silver["⚪ Silver Layer\n（清理、去重、PII遮蔽）"]
        C1[缺值處理\ndropna / ffill / fillna]
        C2[去重複\ndrop_duplicates\ndropDuplicatesWithinWatermark]
        C3[異常值移除\nIQR fence / z-score clip]
        C4[PII 遮蔽/假名化]
        C5[型別轉換 & Regex抽取]
        C6[Schema drift 偵測]
    end

    subgraph Gold["🟡 Gold Layer\n（聚合、分析就緒）"]
        D[分析用資料集\nFeature Store]
    end

    A1 & A2 & A3 & A4 & A5 --> B
    B --> C1 & C2 & C3 & C4 & C5 & C6
    C1 & C2 & C3 & C4 & C5 & C6 --> D

    style Bronze fill:#8B4513,color:#fff
    style Silver fill:#C0C0C0,color:#000
    style Gold fill:#DAA520,color:#000
